{
  "stem": "13623.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we see the gallows, the rope with a noose standing there with a bench for the prisoners to stand up on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And all of us had to stand there in a circle, and we all have to watch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "One of the prisoners started to talk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he was telling us not to worry, to hold out, the war is lost, the Germans are going to lose.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And as he was starting to talk, the SS stopped him, stifled him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The man didn't have anything to lose anymore anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He knew in a few minutes he's dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Where he was talking as much as he could until he was stopped.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the two prisoners were hung.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That's the first time that I saw an execution of this kind in the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I saw that people-- I got used to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was hardened already by that point to see dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I never saw anybody get hung before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Several times after that, within a period of several weeks in-- in between, some of the prisoners that worked in those V1 and V2 place knew what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they sabotaged the work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because they sabotaged the work, they were put in-- they were put in-- there was a jail in the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They were put into jail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The night before they would gag them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They would put a-- a gag in their mouth because of what happened before when that guy was talking, I guess.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So with that gag all night in their mouth-- it must have been done real tight-- when they came out to be hung, they were all swollen around this gag.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They tried to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I remember hearing like muffled noises that they wanted to say something.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
